TEXT 1752 -536 Left 2 ;https://poujouly.net/2015/09/22/modulation-fm-avec-ltspice/\n \nFvco(t) = space + VFM(t) * (mark - space)\nVFM(t)  = 0 ==>  Fvco(t)= space \nVFM(t)  = 1 ==>  Fvco(t)= mark\n \nFvco(t) = fmin + V_out_PI * (fmax - fmin)\nV_out_PI =0     ==> Fvco = fmin\nV_out_PI =1     ==> Fvco = fmax\nV_out_PI =0.5  ==> Fvco = (fmax+fmin)/2
